						<summary>

						<p>On a pillar in the Pāṭaḷa-Nāgēśvara temple.</p>						

						<p>This is an undated inscription in late characters.</p>						

						<p>Records the obeisance of Mūla Rāghava-bhaṭlu, son of Yaṟu (Yeṟṟa)-bhaṭlu and grandson of Jagu-bhaṭlu to god Pātāḷa-Nāgēśvara.</p>						

